  <brief_title>Effect of Combination Therapy With Two Drugs (Colesevelam and Ezetimibe) in Patients With High Cholesterol</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel-Group Study of the Efficacy and Safety of WelChol® in Combination With Zetia® Compared to Zetia® Alone in Patients With Primary Hypercholesterolemia</official_title>
